::: {.noteText}
IX AN EVOLUTION OF IDOLS
:::

::: {.sectionHeading}
X - An Evolution of Phenomena
:::

::: {.noteHeading}
Highlight ([orange]{.highlight_orange}) - Location 717
:::

::: {.noteText}
X THE EVOLUTION OF PHENOMENA
:::

::: {.noteHeading}
Highlight ([orange]{.highlight_orange}) - Location 718
:::

::: {.noteText}
It is only necessary to take the first feeble step towards a renewal of
participation---that is, the bare acknowledgement in beta-thinking that
phenomena are collective representations---in order to see that the
actual evolution of the earth we know must have been at the same time an
evolution of consciousness.
:::

